{"tid":328032,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"芭堤雅3日遊有感","createTime":"2017-07-19T09:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T04:07:50.000Z","uid":65892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ff6ad3835b6d3a2e4a57ec5e91ad4cf0f778ff","tid":328032,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"係酒店天台泳池舒舒服服享受緊，一班大陸人同香港人一黎就嘈到仆街，仲周圍坐同圍放野，三九唔識七坐係你張椅尾做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點鬼佬都頂唔順，走晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，住個間siam@siam真係唔錯，天台泳池真係冠絕附近所有酒店，對面又有big c，又有小食檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce516b09ba74f56ed61a2c3aed05e8e239119de","tid":328032,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"有咩好食？好睇？必去？"},{"pid":"de3c11de40540f11cf8d73ae828da94864719596","tid":328032,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩好食？好睇？必去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想獵奇可以去walking street，好似連真人性愛show都有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n野食就無咩特別了，多數留係酒店到享受，可以去睇下人妖show同老虎show。"},{"pid":"51c9634d0be8ff4bfdf19ac2667600a0acc9b7d7","tid":328032,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"三九唔識七坐係你張椅尾做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8c8def9a427005bf7c71990f5342cad284d633","tid":328032,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三九唔識七坐係你張椅尾做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知，自己係到玩手機，望住都唔走，大陸撚黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03aec37650259d30d243088f5a86a687958941af","tid":328032,"uid":33478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"唔凍咩天台泳池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}